lead_paragraph: Benfica's Eduardo Salvio converted a penalty and Dynamo Kiev missed one as the Portuguese side won 1-0 on Tuesday to go level on points with Napoli at the top of their Champions League group.

headline.print_headline: Salvio Penalty Hands Benfica Victory Over Kiev
